# OpenLogo example 01: movement
# level 1 introduces the turtle heading pen and color.

clear_screen
set_color "blue"
set_width 3

# draw three sides of a path with full command names.
forward 80
right 90
forward 80
left 90
back 30

# lift the pen to move without drawing then return home.
pen_up
home
pen_down

# expected final state: turtle at the origin with heading 0 pen down blue width 3.
